instructions: Set the table cloth and place the place on top of the cloth
Place the plate first then the salad plate on top of the dinner plate
On top of the salad plate place the napkin on top
Grab the wine glass and set it on the top right corner
Place the water glass on the right side of the wine glass
Place the salad fork on the left side of both plates
Place the dinner fork next to the salad fork on the right side
Grab the dinner knife and place it on the right side of both plates
Grab the soup spoon and place it on the right side of the knife
